    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It's in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
